sitting together the hostess sits to the left of the seat that is 
properly hers is that clear 
now if the women are served before the men the woman on the 
hosts right is served first and the woman on the hosts left is 
served second try explaining that to the servants 
one also should be aware that an invitation for 8 oclock doesnt 
necessarily mean you show up at 8 in some countries its a signal 
to turn up at 930 
at official dinners in certain commonwealth countries it is 
rude to smoke at the table before the toast to the queen and 
